data.description: This house offers country living at its finest! This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with over 2000 sq ft has it all! Large kitchen has a spacious island and french doors leading out to a covered patio. Family room has a vaulted ceiling with a view of the staircase, and a beautiful floor to ceiling rock fireplace. Spacious master bath has dual sinks, large shower and marble counter tops. Outside you will find multiple outbuildings, a stock tanks, pens for livestock and a huge Pavilion on a slab perfect for entertaining. Workshop has electricity and plenty of space for storage, plus a separate storage shed. New Roof installed September 1st 2023.
